name: Pasar Malem
description:
Pasar Malem is a cheap version of a carnival event in my Country (Indonesia).In which there are stands for games and selling food. Pasar Malem is usually held in an open field. In order to attract the public's interest.Pasar Malem are held at night and usually last for several days.
